Video taken from patrol car dashcam captures 'end of days' group brawling with cops in Cottonwood, Arizona, on March 21 . 
  Enoch Gaver, 21, was killed in the fight and Sgt Jeremy Daniels was shot in the leg . 
  David Gaver was also shot but has since been released from hospital . 
